## ğŸ—ï¸ Architecture

### Multi-Agent Components

#### 1. Intent Recognition
- **Location**: `app/engine/intent/`
- **Purpose**: Classify user intent (Social, Informational, Objection, etc.)
- **Technology**: Context-Aware Intent Classifier

#### 2. Task Orchestration
- **Location**: `app/engine/coordinator/`
- **Purpose**: Route tasks to appropriate agents
- **Technology**: LangGraph Dynamic Workflow + Contextual Bandit

#### 3. Tool Calling
- **Location**: `app/tools/`
- **Purpose**: Execute tools with self-correction
- **Features**: Rate limiting, caching, reflection

#### 4. Memory Management
- **Location**: `app/engine/memory/`
- **Purpose**: 4-tier memory system
- **Tiers**: S0 (short-term), S1 (session), S2 (user profile), S3 (global)

### Agent Implementations

- **Coach Agent** (`app/agents/ask/coach_agent.py`): Real-time feedback with SOP grounding
- **NPC Simulator** (`app/agents/practice/npc_simulator.py`): Realistic customer personas
- **Strategy Analyzer** (`app/agents/evaluate/strategy_analyzer.py`): Performance evaluation

